'''Inez''' is a neighbor of [[JJ Lau]].

==History==
Inez was one of the residents evacuated from The Langham. After she was evacuated, she talked to JJ and Dean. She noticed that Dean wasn't checking on her as much as he was JJ. She also told Dean about [[Seth (Station 19)|Seth]], JJ's sometimes boyfriend.
